Are you a recent or soon-to-be Bachelor's / Master's / PhD graduate? This Friday (10/18) at 1:30-2PM Pacific Time, my team is hosting an informational session about Microsoft AI Development Acceleration Program — an early-in-career program for new graduates to gain exposure to a diverse set of AI opportunities at Microsoft. 

Read more about the program here: https://lnkd.in/emKYMrE

Click on the link below to join the info session: https://lnkd.in/gfr8Zz9
history.subject: Microsoft AI Development Acceleration Program Info Session
